Package com.zoomly.model

Class Vehicle

java.lang.Object
com.zoomly.model.Vehicle
public class Vehicle extends Object
Vehicle.java Model class representing a vehicle. Stores information related to a vehicle, such as VIN, make, model, year, mileage, price per day, image path, and description. Used for interacting with the vehicle data in the database.
